id: branding-uniformity-policy
severity: critical
description: "All brand logo/symbol representations must match the official production shape exactly"
guard: "ALL BRAND LOGOS AND SYMBOLS ACROSS ALL SYSTEMS MUST MATCH THE OFFICIAL PRODUCTION SHAPE. No custom SVG polygons, no Unicode symbol substitutes, no CSS-drawn approximations."
rules:
  - Every brand logo must use the exact official icon - no custom reproductions
  - SVG polygon approximations are FORBIDDEN for brand logos
  - Unicode symbol characters as brand logos are FORBIDDEN
  - CSS-drawn brand shapes are FORBIDDEN
  - All existing non-compliant brand representations must be migrated
